Table monthly_canvas_campaign_classifications

The \'monthly_canvas_campaign_classifications\' table contains data about the monthly classifications of various marketing campaigns. It includes details such as the advertiser, campaign, placement, and region. This data can be used to analyze the performance of different campaigns, placements, and regions. It can also help in understanding the marketing mix and identifying the most effective channels and tactics for each advertiser. This information can be useful for marketing teams to optimize their campaigns and allocate resources accordingly.
